The theorem statement `Φ₃_integrableOn {r : ℝ} (hr : r ≥ 0) : IntegrableOn (Φ₃ r) (Ioc (0 : ℝ) 1) volume := by ...` is using the `IntegrableOn` definition. Looking at the definition of `IntegrableOn`, it requires two things:
